Step 1 - npm create vite@latest
Step 2 - your project
Step 3 - react then javascript
Step 4 - cd project name (go into project folder)
Step 5 - npm install
Step 6 - npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
Step 7 - npx tailwindcss init -p
Step 8 - write in tailwind.config
         export default {
            content: [
                  "./index.html",
                  "./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
            ],
            theme: {
                  extend: {},
            },
            plugins: [],
         }
Step 9 - write in index.css file is 
         @tailwind base;
         @tailwind components;
         @tailwind utilities;
Step 10 - npm run dev
